	   <tr><td colspan=2>Here is where they come from:<br><br>They are drops while doing a quest.&nbsp;&nbsp;They quest giver is in PoT.  He and She, there are two people together, are Erudites.  They hang out in the shake on the coast with the rest of the hippies meditating.  One is laying down as if knocked out cold.<br><br>Hail the man, he is the knocked out one.  Yadda yadda yadda, then talk to the women was she starts to talk.  Talk this, talk that.  She mentions you must find the mans planier form. His form is in the Plane of Nightmares.  <br><br>Zone into the PoN and once ready go LEFT.  Follow the zone wall passed the Hobgoblins and keep going.  You will end up running up to what looks like a large hedge.  Just on the other side of this hedge will be the mans Planier form.  Same name as the man passed out in PoT.<br><br>You are going to enter his dream to get a jeweled dagger.  Talk to him,  make sure group leader is the one character flagged.  Once you enter his dream follow him and protect him.  You will be jumped at 1st be single lvl60 MoBs.  TRY to stay in the center of the isleway you will be walking down.  Easy to get aggro of other MoBS through the wall.  <br><br>The NPC is a bad ass himself so he doesnt need a WHOLE lot of attention.  After a few singles then a few doulbes.  Hit hard and fast.  They are Werewolf looking things, bigger and stronger then the ones that wander the zone.  THESE bad boys drop the bows.  Also drop Blue Diamonds and normal Diamonds.<br><br>We never finished the quest.  Got to the part were we were hit by 4 MoBs and end of story =)<br><br>Hope that helps some.  We got two bows and not a single Ranger in the group.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
